WEBVTT

00:08.163 --> 00:09.580
A turtle.

00:09.581 --> 00:11.582
A turtle's taking a walk
in Central Park... Oh.

00:11.583 --> 00:13.066
Yeah. late one night.
Uh-huh.

00:13.067 --> 00:15.703
And he gets mugged
by a gang of snails.

00:15.704 --> 00:17.088
Uh-oh.
Now...

00:17.089 --> 00:20.074
the investigating detective
asks the turtle,

00:20.075 --> 00:22.793
"What-what can you recall?"
And the turtle thinks,

00:22.794 --> 00:24.912
looks confused,
and he says,

00:24.913 --> 00:28.215
"I don't know.
It happened so fast."

00:29.451 --> 00:32.153
Y-you know,
Walter,

00:32.154 --> 00:34.422
it's great that
your jokes are always clean.

00:34.423 --> 00:36.490
Be nice if they were funny, too.

00:36.491 --> 00:37.775
What is not funny about that?

00:37.776 --> 00:39.160
Everything.
I'd say the set up,

00:39.161 --> 00:41.262
the punch line, the delivery:
the whole thing.

00:42.564 --> 00:44.115
Walt.
It's a turtle!

00:44.116 --> 00:47.118
Give it up, Walter.
Was everything satisfactory, gentlemen?

00:47.119 --> 00:48.936
Toughest piece of meat
I ever had, Karl.

00:48.937 --> 00:51.205
What did you do,
run over it on the way to work?

00:51.206 --> 00:52.706
I'm sorry

00:52.707 --> 00:54.492
it was not to your liking,
Commissioner.

00:54.493 --> 00:56.343
Uh, may I offer
another round

00:56.344 --> 00:57.945
of Appletinis on the house?

00:57.946 --> 00:59.213
Oh, thank you, Karl.

00:59.214 --> 01:01.115
We'll tip the full five percent.

01:01.116 --> 01:02.683
Wait a minute, Frank.
What are you doing, huh? No, I got it.

01:02.684 --> 01:04.468
No, I got this, all right?
Frank!

01:04.468 --> 01:06.286
Hold on a second.
Um... Thank you.

01:06.287 --> 01:07.488
Um...

01:07.489 --> 01:09.507
The atrium

01:09.508 --> 01:11.225
at John Jay College is, uh...

01:11.226 --> 01:12.927
being dedicated

01:12.928 --> 01:15.162
to the memory of my son.
Oh...

01:17.432 --> 01:19.767
It's a pretty big deal.

01:19.768 --> 01:21.602
The ceremony's Thursday.

01:21.603 --> 01:24.505
Oh, I-I wouldn't
miss it, Frank.

01:24.506 --> 01:27.191
I'll be there, absolutely.
Sure.

01:27.192 --> 01:28.642
Done.

01:28.643 --> 01:30.194
Thank you.

01:36.785 --> 01:38.986
I need a little time.

01:40.155 --> 01:42.957
Life is good, Walter.

01:42.958 --> 01:44.491
Where did you get these?

01:44.492 --> 01:45.526
Don't ask.

